1. *Bio* je lijep dan (It was a beautiful day).
2. On je *bio* tamo (He was there).
3. On je *bio* stari prijatelj (He was an old friend).
4. On je *bio* učenik (He was a student).
5. On je *bio* na poslu (He was at work).
6. Njegov otac je *bio* vojnik (His father was a soldier).
7. Ona je *bila* tamo (She was there).
8. Ona je *bila* lijepa žena (She was a beautiful woman).
9. Ona je *bila* učiteljica (She was a teacher).
10. Ona je *bila* u školi (She was in school).